General.Name: Distoken Acquisition Corporation Ordinary Shares
General.Description: Distoken Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, recapitalization, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to acquire businesses in the technology industry primarily in Asia. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Kunming, China.
